summary:
I'm a passionate and driven woman. 
I’m curious and open-minded. 
I love Mozart. And at the same time The Queen and André Hazes. 
I’m a fan of IT gadgets and innovations as well as of psychology. 
And I like soccer. 
I've climbed the career ladder and I reached heights with hard work, of which I'm proud. I'm a loyal professional with a broad range of experiences in business development and general management. I’m exceptional in sales, negotiation, consulting and in coaching. 
I lived already in 4 countries, so I speak various languages and I’m familiar with different cultures as well. 
The last 2 years I spent at home with my baby daughter and now off to a fresh new start.
